channel.title: Problem with new shops
channel.description:
I have a problem with my shops. Untill about a week ago, all shops worked fine. But when i try to add new shops, i can not open them. And when trying to use a other npc for a working excisting shop, it wont work either. But when putting the old npc back, it works again :confused: Anyone got an idea of what the problem may be? It is really anoying
Edit: Untill a week ago all newly added shops worked normal, but now they stopped working too O.o
